WEBVTT

00:00.190 --> 00:02.190
Previously on The Originals...

00:02.190 --> 00:04.980
I need your help, Caroline.
Hope is dying.

00:04.980 --> 00:06.520
She consumed the dark magic,

00:06.520 --> 00:07.900
<i>and now it's consuming her.</i>

00:07.900 --> 00:09.730
She won't survive
tonight's full moon.

00:09.730 --> 00:10.810
She triggered her curse?

00:10.810 --> 00:12.520
<i>I need your daughters.</i>

00:12.520 --> 00:14.690
They're siphoner witches.
It's what they were born to do.

00:14.690 --> 00:18.140
Siphon magic from one thing...
And put it in another.

00:18.140 --> 00:19.020
When you're mid-transformation,

00:19.020 --> 00:20.690
<i>the Saltzman girls will be able</i>

00:20.690 --> 00:22.400
<i>to siphon the magic out of you.</i>

00:22.400 --> 00:23.270
Are you sure about this?

00:23.270 --> 00:24.810
I'll dispose of the magic later.

00:24.810 --> 00:26.810
After they siphon it from Hope,

00:26.810 --> 00:28.270
what are they supposed
to do with it?

00:28.270 --> 00:30.230
They'll put it in me.
When the power is in me,

00:30.230 --> 00:32.140
<i>there's only one way</i>

00:32.140 --> 00:33.520
to make sure it's gone for good.

00:33.520 --> 00:35.140
Someone needs to kill me.

00:35.140 --> 00:37.100
<i>Niklaus.</i>

00:38.190 --> 00:39.270
Don't.

00:40.730 --> 00:42.140
Put it down.

00:42.140 --> 00:43.900
Walk away, Elijah.
You shouldn't be here for this.

00:43.900 --> 00:45.560
Put it down and let's talk.

00:45.560 --> 00:46.980
There's nothing left to say.

00:46.980 --> 00:48.560
It's time to end this chapter,

00:48.560 --> 00:50.100
get rid of the dark magic
once and for all.

00:50.100 --> 00:51.600
Dad?

00:52.980 --> 00:54.560
What's going on here?

00:56.440 --> 00:58.900
Get her out of here.

00:58.900 --> 01:01.350
Your death is not the answer.
Death?

01:01.350 --> 01:04.810
Wh-What are you talking about?

01:04.810 --> 01:07.690
They put it into you.

01:09.140 --> 01:11.690
But you told me that they put it
into something safe,

01:11.690 --> 01:14.560
and instead, you use
my first transition to trick me.

01:14.560 --> 01:16.560
So what happens,

01:16.560 --> 01:19.140
you just kill yourself
and the magic goes away?

01:20.810 --> 01:23.020
And you're gonna let him go
through with this? I don't need

01:23.020 --> 01:24.730
his permission
to save your life!

01:24.730 --> 01:26.640
Come back with me
to New Orleans, Niklaus.

01:26.640 --> 01:29.560
We'll find another way. We both
know that's not gonna happen.

01:30.600 --> 01:32.480
I'm sorry, Hope.

01:32.480 --> 01:34.640
I've made my decision.

01:34.640 --> 01:36.600
And I've made mine.

